Name: Dodge Diego
About the game: Dodge Diego is a side-scrolling adventure jump and run where you play Diego, a young man on a mission. You will follow Diego on his journey through a jungle full of enemies and other dangers. Skeletons and scary monsters will try to stop you, but you will prove that you truly are the toughest of the jungle, or will you? The soundtrack composed by Eric Skiff will motivate you to improve your highscore over and over again. How far can you go?
